data.description: Welcome to your inviting single-family ranch nestled in a serene neighborhood! This delightful abode offers a perfect blend of comfort and style, featuring 3 spacious bedrooms and 1 bath, all adorned with gleaming hardwood floors that exude warmth and elegance. The charming shiplap accents add character, creating a cozy ambiance that you'll love coming home to. Your peace of mind is ensured with a young roof and newer windows, providing both durability and energy efficiency. The attached single garage not only offers convenient parking but also boasts a versatile loft space, ideal for storage or even a home office or hobby area. Venture downstairs to discover the full partially finished basement, offering ample room for recreation, hobbies, or additional living space tailored to your needs. Whether it's a cozy family room, a home gym, or a play area for the kids, the possibilities are endless. With its desirable location and thoughtful features, this charming ranch presents an opportunity you won't want to miss. Come and experience the comfort and convenience of this wonderful home – schedule your showing today!
